snippet.title: Tower of Fantasy - Pre-Order Trailer | PS5™ & PS4®
snippet.description:
Experience the vastness of the world, master diverse combat mechanics, and unlock the potential of simulacrum characters. Prepare to unleash your inner Wanderer on PlayStation®!
Pre-order begins on June 20th（UTC+0）, so mark your calendars and be ready to embark on this epic adventure.

Follow our social media to stay tuned for PS Exclusive News
